      <title>欧洲股市止跌，因业绩和拜登消息成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/european-stocks-snap-losses-as-earnings-biden-news-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者评估企业盈利结果以及乔·拜登退出美国总统竞选的决定，欧洲股市上涨，结束了一周的下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/european-stocks-snap-losses-as-earnings-biden-news-in-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 07:28:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登退出竞选，支持哈里斯，哈里斯努力争取支持 - Daybreak: 欧洲 07/22/2024</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-22/daybreak-europe-07-22-2024-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博日报欧洲版是您保持领先地位的必看早间新闻。我们从伦敦现场直播，为您安排一天的日程，为您带来美国和亚洲隔夜市场新闻。我们会告诉您欧洲投资者最关心的问题，让您在交易开始前获得深刻见解。
今天的嘉宾：苏黎世联邦理工学院证券研究中心欧洲-大西洋安全高级研究员 Gorana Grgic 和全球战略项目总监兼全球战略顾问 Marco Vicenzino。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-22/daybreak-europe-07-22-2024-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 07:21:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维旺迪选择伦敦证券交易所收购 Canal+ 股票，阿姆斯特丹收购 Havas 股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/vivendi-picks-lse-for-canal-stock-amsterdam-for-havas-in-split</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着法国亿万富翁文森特·博洛雷 (Vincent Bolloré) 推进拆分其庞大的媒体和娱乐帝国的计划，维旺迪集团 (Vivendi SE) 表示，旗下 Canal+ 广播业务应该在伦敦证券交易所上市，而 Havas 广告公司也可能会在阿姆斯特丹交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/vivendi-picks-lse-for-canal-stock-amsterdam-for-havas-in-split</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 07:16:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着自由港液化天然气重启，欧洲天然气价格跌至一周以来的最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/european-gas-falls-to-lowest-in-a-week-as-freeport-lng-restarts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着德克萨斯州自由港液化天然气工厂部分重启，供应风险减弱，欧洲天然气价格跌至一周以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/european-gas-falls-to-lowest-in-a-week-as-freeport-lng-restarts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 07:15:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰与债券持有人委员会达成债务重组协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/ukraine-bondholders-committee-reach-debt-restructuring-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰与部分私人债权人达成原则协议，将重组超过 200 亿美元的国际债务，此举可使这个饱受战争蹂躏的国家避免债务违约，并节省资金用于与俄罗斯的战斗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/ukraine-bondholders-committee-reach-debt-restructuring-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 07:09:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡本周将在华盛顿会见拜登</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-22/a-confident-netanyahu-takes-his-message-to-washington-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登将于周二在椭圆形办公室接见以色列总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡。内塔尼亚胡还将在访问期间向国会发表讲话。彭博社的 Stuart Livingston-Wallace 与 Joumanna Bercetche 就“中东和非洲展望”进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-22/a-confident-netanyahu-takes-his-message-to-washington-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 06:17:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国精炼铜出口量因供应过剩而翻番创纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/china-s-refined-copper-exports-double-to-record-on-local-surplus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球最大金属买家的需求疲软，促使冶炼厂转向海外市场，中国精炼铜出口上个月飙升至创纪录水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/china-s-refined-copper-exports-double-to-record-on-local-surplus</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 03:41:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登退出竞选导致美元下跌；股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/dollar-edges-lower-following-biden-s-election-exit-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登结束竞选连任并支持副总统卡马拉·哈里斯后，美元下跌，美国国债上涨。欧洲股市从今年最糟糕的一周反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/dollar-edges-lower-following-biden-s-election-exit-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 22:55:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伍德赛德将斥资 9 亿美元收购 Tellurian，押注天然气需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/woodside-to-buy-us-lng-developer-tellurian-for-900-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伍德赛德能源集团有限公司 (Woodside Energy Group Ltd.) 同意以约 9 亿美元收购陷入困境的美国液化天然气出口项目开发商 Tellurian Inc.，押注全球对该燃料的需求将快速增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/woodside-to-buy-us-lng-developer-tellurian-for-900-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 22:42:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
